Krita is an open source and community-driven tool for digital art, animation, and visual storytelling. Our goal is to empower artists everywhere, and of all skill levels, to realize their creative vision without gatekeepers or socioeconomic hurdles. Development is only made possible thanks to the ongoing feedback and contributions from our amazing community of artists and developers.
You can get Krita, learn more, or get involved by visiting https://krita.org! And you can support the project by joining our development fund at https://fund.krita.org/.
